Should be possible with TDA1541 driver, but you should try the hifiberry driver in the current raspberry pi 3.10 and 3.12 kernel. No compilation needed. Just do a "sudo rpi-update" and load these modules:
snd_soc_bcm2708_i2s
bcm2708_dmaengine
snd_soc_pcm5102a
snd_soc_hifiberry_dacï»¿
